Placeholder: The Grainway Station

A placeholder encounter for the Grainway Station arc.

choices:

* Explore = Search the depot [requires meets combat 5]
    @if check combat medium {
        You find something valuable.
        +add_item mountain_regiment_armor
        +finish_dungeon
    } @else {
        It doesn't go well.
        +add_condition injured
        +finish_dungeon
    }

* Negotiate = Talk your way through [requires meets combat 5]
    @if check negotiation medium {
        You find something valuable.
        +add_item mountain_regiment_armor
        +finish_dungeon
    } @else {
        It doesn't go well.
        +add_condition injured
        +finish_dungeon
    }

* Depart = Leave this place behind
    You depart Grainway Station.
    +flee_dungeon
